Press & Events

DJO® Launches New DonJoy® IceMan CLASSIC3™

September 16, 2019

   Vista, CA September 16, 2019 – DJO, LLC (“DJO” or the “Company”), a
   leading global provider of medical technologies designed to get and
   keep people moving, announces the launch of the new DonJoy® IceMan
   CLASSIC3™ cold therapy unit that helps reduce pain and swelling through
   controlled delivery of extended cold therapy.

DJO® announces release of AltiVate Reverse® Short Stem, the first fully
convertible, inlay, short stem shoulder replacement system in the United
States

July 16, 2019

   Its bone-sparing short-stem and innovative 135° neck-shaft angle sits
   entirely within the humerus, allowing for easy conversion from anatomic
   to reverse shoulder arthroplasty.
